    Package Description
    com.cas.activity
    This package contains all the activity classes
    com.cas.fragment
    This package contains the fragment activities for the course/exercise selection screen.
    com.cas.model
    The model package contains all the models for parsing the JSON string from the moodle server.
    com.cas.server
    This package contains all the classes used for communicating with the Moodle server

    This package contains misc utility classes.
